reviewText: Guys gone wild fresh meat offers plenty of fresh nude men to look at. As others have said there is an issue with the DVD when it plays a scene will freeze. At least it is a scene not hot. Treat yourself to the eye candy.

I ordered this DVD from one supplier. It rendered "skipping damaged area"  in several sections of the DVD.  I returned it.  Then, I re-ordered it with a different supplier with the same results....  The second supplier  sent another replacement. Since I've order GGW DVDs before and nothing like this has ever happened, I concluded it was a manufacturer defect.  It appears this particular title may have been massed produced with the defect.  Unless you know this defect has been acknowledged and corrected, use caution when purchasing this particular title.  Other titles have proved  to be available  from a variety of vendors with acceptable quality....
